Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,慚愧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,perpectual
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,永久的　無休止的
